2. Uththaanam cheythutane thanne kurishiccha
sehiyone nashippicchu, sabhaa paanigrahanatthe
otthuyirin than meshayorukkam cheythathinul
than rakthamathil chertthorapputhrannaayu sthothram;
/tsthothram sleebaayaal veendavanaayu;
/tsthothram chaavaaluyir chertthavanaayu;
sthothram punyatthinu thanu rudhirangal thannavanaayu.
